title: Nvidia’s peace offering isn’t working
description: Nvidia quietly launched the 16GB version of the RTX 4060 Ti. The lack of fanfare might be caused by the card's subpar performance.

title: Pay-with-palm coming to all of Amazon’s Whole Foods Market stores
description: Amazon is expanding its Amazon One palm-recognition system to all 500 of its Whole Foods Market stores in the U.S. by the end of this year.
